[
  {
    "start": 0.001,
    "end": 2.48,
    "text": "**Anna:** This is the {Roosevelt|ルーズベルト家の|/ˈroʊzəvɛlt/} Memorial."
  },
  {
    "start": 2.48,
    "end": 4.4,
    "text": "**Anna:** Where is the {symbol|象徴/記号|/ˈsɪmbəl/}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 5.2,
    "end": 7.84,
    "text": "**Anna:** This game is really {fun|楽しい|/fʌn/|This game is fun for everyone.}"
  },
  {
    "start": 7.84,
    "end": 9.68,
    "text": "**Anna:** You have to {find|見つける|/faɪnd/|Can you find the key?} things that"
  },
  {
    "start": 9.94,
    "end": 11.54,
    "text": "**Anna:** Aren't really there."
  },
  {
    "start": 11.54,
    "end": 20.66,
    "text": "**Anna:** When you find an American {symbol|象徴/記号|/ˈsɪmbəl/}, you win points and a fun fact about a US president."
  },
  {
    "start": 20.66,
    "end": 21.46,
    "text": "**Anna:** Yay!"
  },
  {
    "start": 21.46,
    "end": 23.22,
    "text": "**Anna:** I found {Uncle Sam|アメリカの擬人化キャラクター|/ˈʌŋkəl sæm/}"
  },
  {
    "start": 23.64,
    "end": 26.36,
    "text": "**Anna:** And I won 40 points."
  },
  {
    "start": 26.36,
    "end": 28.279,
    "text": "**Anna:** What is the fun fact?"
  },
  {
    "start": 28.279,
    "end": 33.239,
    "text": "**Voice:** Franklin Roosevelt was the first to {fly|飛ぶ|/flaɪ/|Birds fly in the sky.} in a plane as president."
  },
  {
    "start": 33.64,
    "end": 35.48,
    "text": "**Anna:** I didn't know that."
  },
  {
    "start": 36.239,
    "end": 40.16,
    "text": "**Anna:** This is a really {beautiful|美しい|/ˈbjutəfəl/|What a beautiful day!} memorial."
  },
  {
    "start": 40.16,
    "end": 42.8,
    "text": "**Anna:** This is the Lincoln Memorial."
  },
  {
    "start": 42.8,
    "end": 46.559,
    "text": "**Anna:** Where is the symbol?"
  },
  {
    "start": 46.559,
    "end": 47.839,
    "text": "**Anna:** I found it!"
  },
  {
    "start": 47.839,
    "end": 50.559,
    "text": "**Anna:** The {Statue|像/彫像|/ˈstætʃu/} of Liberty."
  },
  {
    "start": 50.22,
    "end": 52.78,
    "text": "**Anna:** Please give me my fun fact."
  },
  {
    "start": 53.02,
    "end": 55.5,
    "text": "**Voice:** Abraham Lincoln was a great {wrestler|レスラー|/ˈrɛsləʳ/|Wrestlers are strong athletes.}"
  },
  {
    "start": 55.5,
    "end": 56.7,
    "text": "**Anna:** I didn't know that."
  },
  {
    "start": 56.94,
    "end": 60.3,
    "text": "**Anna:** Lincoln wanted {freedom|自由|/ˈfriːdəm/|Freedom is important for everyone.} for all people."
  },
  {
    "start": 60.3,
    "end": 63.82,
    "text": "**Anna:** So the Statue of Liberty works well."
  },
  {
    "start": 63.68,
    "end": 66.64,
    "text": "**Anna:** And I won 20 points."
  },
  {
    "start": 66.64,
    "end": 69.12,
    "text": "**Anna:** Time to find the next symbol."
  },
  {
    "start": 69.76,
    "end": 70.96,
    "text": "**Anna:** Oh!"
  },
  {
    "start": 71.2,
    "end": 72.72,
    "text": "**Dan:** Hey, look out!"
  },
  {
    "start": 72.74,
    "end": 73.62,
    "text": "**Anna:** Sorry."
  },
  {
    "start": 73.62,
    "end": 75.22,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hey, it's you!"
  },
  {
    "start": 75.22,
    "end": 77.3,
    "text": "**Anna:** Now I should be more {careful|注意深い|/ˈkɛrfəl/|Be careful when crossing the street.}"
  },
  {
    "start": 77.3,
    "end": 78.42,
    "text": "**Dan:** That's okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 78.42,
    "end": 80.9,
    "text": "**Anna:** This game is a {lot|たくさん/多い} of fun."
  },
  {
    "start": 80.9,
    "end": 82.34,
    "text": "**Anna:** What's your name?"
  },
  {
    "start": 82.34,
    "end": 83.06,
    "text": "**Dan:** Dan."
  },
  {
    "start": 83.06,
    "end": 84.26,
    "text": "**Dan:** What's yours?"
  },
  {
    "start": 84.26,
    "end": 84.82,
    "text": "**Anna:** Anna"
  },
  {
    "start": 85.14,
    "end": 87.06,
    "text": "**Dan:** Like {Americana|アメリカ文化|/ˌæmərɪˈkɑːnə/}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 87.06,
    "end": 88.9,
    "text": "**Anna:** Yeah, I guess so."
  },
  {
    "start": 88.9,
    "end": 90.74,
    "text": "**Dan:** Did you find any {symbols|記号/シンボル}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 90.74,
    "end": 97.3,
    "text": "**Anna:** Yes, I found three and I won {120|百二十} {points|ポイント}"
  },
  {
    "start": 97.76,
    "end": 102.4,
    "text": "**Dan:** Me too, but did you find the {bald eagle|はげワシ}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 102.4,
    "end": 104.16,
    "text": "**Anna:** No."
  },
  {
    "start": 104.16,
    "end": 105.12,
    "text": "**Dan:** Did you"
  },
  {
    "start": 106.04,
    "end": 107.24,
    "text": "**Anna:** No."
  },
  {
    "start": 107.24,
    "end": 109.64,
    "text": "**Anna:** First one to find it wins!"
  },
  {
    "start": 111.08,
    "end": 114.44,
    "text": "**Dan:** Hey Anna, look out for that {tree|木}!"
  },
  {
    "start": 115.74,
    "end": 120.46,
    "text": "**Anna:** I learned a {lot|多くのこと} about {presidents|大統領} with this game, but I {ought to|〜すべきだ} be more {careful|注意深い/慎重な}."
  },
  {
    "start": 120.46,
    "end": 121.58,
    "text": "**Anna:** Till next time"
  }
]
